      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Eens faufs Kummoss\nar Meera/ irr labbaſs/\nne ka pils Nams ar kan-\njaimeim Lohpeem ar Reekteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Weens faprattigs Kalps\nwaldihs pahr weenu Dehlu/ kas\nKanna Leetu darra/ un tsdallihs\nto Behrno- Mantu ſtarp teem\nBrahteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas kautejamajs Trauks\npahrbanda to Sudrabu/ un tas\nZeplis to Seltn/ bet tas kUngs\npahrmanna tahs Sirdis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Launadarritajs klau-\nfa us blehdigahn Wallodahm /\nweens Melkulis greeſch to Auſi\nus pahrwehrtitahm Mehlehm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "kas to Nabbaggu aptmeijj/\ntas neewa winna Darritajn/ un\nkas pahr winna Behdahm pree-\nzajahs/ tas ne paliks nenose-\ndſigs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Behrnu Behrni irr to\nWezzako Krohnis/ un to Behr-\nnu Jaukums irr winnu Tehwi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Geffim ne klahjahs no\naugſtahms Leetahms runnaht/\nneds Leelam-Kungani ka tam bij\nnelloht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Dahwanas irr ka weene\ndahrgs Akmine tam/ kann ta irr/\nwiffur kurp tas greeſchahs/ tohp\ntas par Gudru turrehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "kas kahdu Grehku apklahi/\ntas mekle Draudsibu/ bet kas mihe Grehkus/ un kas faw-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta Aprahschana makfa\nwairak pee ta Prahtiga/ neka\njimts Sittenu pee weena Geeka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Weens Dumpju-Zehlejs\nmekle tikkat Laununu/ un pret-\nti to taps weens bahrgs Wehst-\nneffis fuhtihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Labbaki irr weenn Laht-\nschu-Mahti fastapt/ kam tee\nBehrni paremtti irr/ neka weenu\nGeffi fatva Geckiba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "kas Launu par Labbu\natmakfa/ no ta pascha Nammi\ntas Launums ne atstahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "kas kildu fahk/ irr itt ka\nkas Uhdens Dainbi paplehſch\ntapehz atkahpees no Bahrscha-\nnas/ pirms tu eekſch tahs ce-\njaukts tohpt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "kas to Besdeewigu tai-\nno/ un to Tattnu pasaudina/ te-\nirr abbi tam KUNGAM pa-\nNegantibu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "ko palihds Geffim t-\nMakfa Rohka Gudribu pirkt-\nkur tomehr winnam Prahta ne-\nmaid.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wens Draugs mihe wi-\nsa Laika/ un weens Brahl-\ntohp Behdu Deenäs atsihts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tain Zilwekam irr u-\nprahtiga Strds/ kas ar Roh-\napfohlahs preeſſch fawu Tuwa-\nku galivodams.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "kas kildu mihe/ ta-\nDu\n"
    }
  ],
